# Proxy all paths to the Streamlit Cloud app and keep plotivy.app in the URL

# Netlify will preserve the path (:splat) and query string. The `200!` forces

# the proxy even if a matching static file exists.

/\* https://plotivy.streamlit.app/:splat 200!

# If you prefer a hard redirect (changes the address bar to streamlit.app), use:

# /\* https://plotivy.streamlit.app/:splat 301!
